metadata.name: Looking for The Summer
metadata.description: Inspired by my love for summer days that we all miss, especially in these cold days of winter. The hot summer and chilling by the pool while having a shark in the next one just creates a priceless vibe to life along with the crazy things that happen over the summer. And after all those moments are finished as the summer flies by, we’ll all reminisce and go “ Looking for The Summer”.
